http://www.cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CAN-2000-1053
Macromedia/Allaire Security Bulletin ASB00-29;
http://www.macromedia.com/v1/handlers/index.cfm?ID=17969"','CAN-2000-1053','','"JRun server version 2.3.x
