임시 방법으로는, \'p-news.php\' 파일로 접근을 제한 하십시오."','"SID : 2140
Nessus ID: 11669, http://cgi.nessus.org/plugins/dump.php3?id=11669
SecuriTeam, http://www.securiteam.com/unixfocus/5MP0S1PA0I.html"','','','P-News version 1.6','','','alert tcp any any -> any 80 (flow:to_server,established; uricontent:"/p-news.php"; nocase; rev:1;)');
