Nessus ID: 11630
Security Focus BugTraq Mailing List, http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2003-05/0155.html"','CAN-2003-0294','7598','PHP-Proxima 6.0 이전버전','','','alert tcp any any -> any 80 (flow:to_server,established; uricontent:"/autohtml.php"; nocase; rev:1;)');
