CERT:TA04-104A, http://www.us-cert.gov/cas/techalerts/TA04-104A.html
CERT-VN:VU#753212, http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/753212
http://downloads.securityfocus.com/vulnerabilities/exploits/04252004.ms04011lsass.c"','CAN-2003-0533','10108','"Microsoft Windows 2000
