xforce web site, http://xforce.iss.net/xforce/xfdb/9588"','CAN-2002-1027','5249','Macromedia Sitespring 1.2.0','','','alert tcp any any -> any 80 (flow:to_server,established; uricontent:"/error/500error.jsp"; nocase; content:"<script"; nocase; rev:1;)');
