http://www.spidynamics.com/whitepapers/Blind_SQLInjection.pdf
http://www.imperva.com/application_defense_center/white_papers/sql_injection_signatures_evasion.html#advanced"','','','','','','alert tcp any any -> any 80 (flow:to_server,established; content:".asp%20and%201=1"; nocase; rev:1;)');
