http://openview.hp.com/"','','14662','"HP OpenViewNetworkNodeManager6.41
HP OpenView Network NodeManager7.01
HP OpenView Network NodeManager7.5"','','','alert tcp any any -> any 80 (flow:to_server,established; uricontent:"/ovcgi/freeipaddrs.ovpl"; nocase; content:"netid="; rev:1;)');
