- 레지스트리에서 컨트롤에 킬 비트(Kill bit)를 설정하는 방법으로 Internet Explorer에서 COM 개체가 실행되지 않게 한다"','Internet Explorer Home Page http://www.microsoft.com/windows/ie/default.mspx Visual Studio 6.0 Multiple COM Object Instantiation http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/44E4AF45.9060905@xsec.org http://www.xsec.org/index.php?module=Releases&act=view&type=1&id=16','"CVE-2006-4494"','"19572"','Microsoft Internet Explorer 6','','','alert tcp any 80 -> any any (flow:to_client,established; content:"CLSID|3A|4682C82A-B2FF-11D0-95A8-00A0C92B77A9"; nocase; rev:1;)');
